Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.30,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister! We want to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about it?! If you do...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She said "sky island"!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.73,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Log Pose is definitely pointing to the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Give me a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.81,0:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.11,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm just taking him up on his offer!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta this town!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! \NForget the promise, take care of them already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take them on, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at them! They're still standing!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.66,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get those clumsy chickens!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This town isn't for dreaming cowards!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the commotion?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Bellamy Pirates \Nare holding a public lynching.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.55,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! \NWhy are you just taking this from them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.60,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight them! Why don't you just beat them up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, lady. They're smart.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They've realized that their \Nopponents are out of their league.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.06,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fighting a strong opponent... \Nit's a disgraceful move, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he has no dignity as a captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's generous these days,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.24,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,giving 30 million Berries for the \Nhead of a worthless ass like him.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zoro, don't take them on, \Nno matter what happens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... are you both...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.55,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctrine of nonresistance... \NSounds nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to being weak, you have no pride.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get into a single fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But your head is full of dreams.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like worms.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A weak-looking shorty worth 30 million...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered what kind of man he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.59,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just a letdown, it's boring!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met cowards like them before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get them out of my face.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're eyesores.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at them!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to move forward \Ninto the new era if you're with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I buy you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it cost to have you come with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.73,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? You're going to buy me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.61,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Join us. It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to say it,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm too good for a team \Nof small fries like you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How stuck up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Their gang is nothing but dumbasses!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hopeless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take those two and beat it already
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're still alive, you small fries!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't ever come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky island exists.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry pies here really are the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so angry, young lady?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.23,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who won the fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You'll surpass us?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again when we \Nbecome distinguished pirates.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sharp retort was really something, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.09,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The new era they're talking about is crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.77,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The era where pirates have dreams \Nwill be over, they say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.86,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People's dreams... have no end!!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you suddenly shouting about?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about people's dreams?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Outdoing others isn't easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Has your brain melted?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I hear a ruckus outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.81,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother. Those guys might be goin' \Non a rampage 'cause they're pissed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They can go ahead and laugh at us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When you aim high, you sometimes \Ncome across fights not worth fighting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, looks like I interrupted you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he might've known \Nsomething about the sky island.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.01,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... And it's not "he."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.34,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's not "he"? Then what?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"They," probably...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.77,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean there were others with him? \NWhere?! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.24,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The drinks sure taste good today!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.25,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Panel!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.13,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nail!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.76,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.93,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Panel!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.27,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.66,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously... I know I'm repeating myself, \Nbut I'm not a shipwright.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're really handy with stuff, Usopp.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I?! That's the amazing thing about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just buy a new ship instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.16,0:10:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\an8}Are you nuts?! Do you know how we got this ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I've heard it so many times.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was given to you guys by a \Npretty girl from your village, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.75,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, it's dangerous to keep \Ntraveling on a ship in this condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm repairing it! \NGive us a hand here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.34,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Repair? You call this repair? \NYou're just patching it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a funny face, Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... About tonight's dinner...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you don't want any?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.36,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahhh!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.82,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahhh! We do!! Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.61,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I wonder how the seagull stock soup is coming along.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please let us eat!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.33,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.83,0:11:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.32,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with that ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This song is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,L-L-L-L-Luffy! Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wounded?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-D-Doctor!!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So check them out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.81,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what kind of Moguera monster did you fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.65,0:12:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates. But that's okay, it's all over now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.15,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.11,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's over for you guys, \Nit's not over for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you guys?! You're men, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.66,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone provokes you, you should \Njust go ahead and beat them all up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.03,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, better yet, why not just \Nblow up this whole annoying town!!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So what was that stuff you said earlier?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.17,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's past is past! \NDon't talk about ancient history!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to floor you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.77,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's she in such a mood \Nabout when she's unhurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.93,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Did you get any \Ninformation about the sky island?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky... island...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! All I did was mention "sky island,"
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the entire bar broke out laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something funny?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ketchup Star!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard Point!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.66,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite lively up there. \NWhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Welcome back, Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.08,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to eat first, \Nor shall I prepare your bath?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Robin, did you go somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.88,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I got some clothes and \Ninformation about the sky island.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You, Robin!!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This all happened because you \Nstarted talking about that sky island!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't exist,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Chopper!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you to a watery grave!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, leave her alone for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.19,0:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you'd better not get close to her. \NJust don't rock the boat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.49,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Isn't it just an ordinary map? Where is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The town drawn on the left is \NMock Town, where we are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see an x on the other side, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that a man who doesn't \Nblend in in Jaya lives there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't blend in?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Montblanc Cricket.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who talked about dreams \Nand was driven out of this town.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have something in common to discuss.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we try going there?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.43,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec, Luffy. \NI'm not sure if we should go now because...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper, you saw it earlier, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're such a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nami was...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What about me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You tryin' to say I'm some simple-minded idiot?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big boss! Undersea preparations complete!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The mic's ready, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Starting the search sonar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Utan Diver Number 27! \NSonar response confirmed!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,School of fish detected at 9 o'clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.84,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,From it's swimming speed, \Nwe've determined that it's saury.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! \NWe'll have them roasted whole for dinner!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Diver Number 4! \NSonar response confirmed!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Small sailing vessel detected traveling on the sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! A vessel? \NDetermine the exact direction!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.61,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I'd say it's at 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already close enough to see!!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the search and return to the ship, Utan Divers!!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't take long for us to \Ncome across something weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look like the \Nsame guys from before, Usopp.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whether that's a good thing \Nor a bad thing is another story.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we did see them! Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.89,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NAs we thought, that salvager is from this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw his ship coming back!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... but I don't mind seeing him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.37,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, you guys! Quit mumbling over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Honestly, I got all worked up \Nwondering who you guys were!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a reckless face you've got! \NWhat species are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm human, you moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.51,0:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You punks! Don't you know Shojo-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the big boss of the Shojo Pirates \Nand the king of undersea search!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make our big boss angry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.31,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're pirates.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.36,0:17:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that Crocodile, one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea, was defeated?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.57,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you consider my abilities, \Nthat post may come to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been getting all worked \Nup waiting to be contacted.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Then you want to become one \Nof the Seven Warlords of the Sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.96,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, the great part about me
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.67,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I haven't had my hair \Ncut in all my 25 years of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, aren't you surprised?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.93,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.81,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now... What you say \Nreally gets me all worked up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.81,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. You will come out of the tunnel \Nthat is my anger into a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, whatever... \Nbut there's a place we wanna go.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So move aside.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! This area is my turf!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna pass through, pay the toll!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.50,0:18:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he mean by his turf? \NHe's talking like Masira.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did Masira say stuff like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Masira?! What about Masira?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.14,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We kicked him off our boat, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kicked... Kicked...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.01,0:18:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Big boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicked?! How dare you do that to my brother?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is revenge for Masira!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We kicked him, but he's still alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound wave!!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Havoc Sonar!!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what're they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Big boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you use that technique on the ship, it'll...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? But it's amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, no! He's blinded by anger!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's destroying their ship with his voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.56,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone! Stop gawking and \Nlet's get through here while we can!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami's not a demon any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she should be calmer \Nafter letting off that much steam.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey... hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! \NThe waves made it to this ship after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's starting to fall apart, \Nparticularly the repaired areas!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's body is worn out enough as it is!!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stay here, the ship will be torn apart!!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.65,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead! \NTo someplace out of his voice's reach!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this pretty woman says,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.97,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tell me where this Cricket lives!"
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bold woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bold? Well, she was strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She had these mysterious \Nhands popping out everywhere,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.53,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and they knocked down everyone in the bar. \NIt wasn't funny!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does she want with old geezer Cricket?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea around there is the turf \Nof the big monkey brothers.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if you have something \Nto do with that old geezer,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll catch his stupidity.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What that woman's after is \Ngold bullion, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold bullion?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NI heard some gold bullion was found recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say about gold bullion?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.07,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That Cricket guy... \NI'd definitely like to meet him, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me all about him!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.95,0:23:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is, uh... what's his name again?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.91,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Montblanc Cricket.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.96,0:23:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his house, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.37,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a picture book! \NIt's titled "Noland the Liar"!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's a cool name!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that brings back memories. \NI read it a lot when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.05,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard that he was a real person.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Legendary Family! \N'Noland the Liar'
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
